A measure of average random motion of atoms and molecules in an object.

## Ideal Gas

$\left<\frac{mv^2}{2}\right>=\frac{3}{2}k_BT$

where $k_B=1.381\times 10^{-23}\frac{J}{K}$ and angle brackets signify the average value.

